w inquiry by invoking the questions that once directed them: What are we? What is our place in the world? What concerns are appropriate to being here?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 0aMind and body. 0aPhilosophy. 4aCultural Studies : Cultural Critique. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Metaphysics.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791486719423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791486719/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles